{"type":"article","id":18204,"title":"共產黨將國族身份和政治綑綁得真成功","uid":15231,"topics":[5262,7673],"contents":"昨天在Facebook上有人發了有關中國捐贈物資的照片到Subtle Asian Traits.&nbsp;<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/OPSHxtc.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OPSHxtc.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/OPSHxtc.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n結果激起了一堆亞裔青年(大多在西方國家居住)的怒氣<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/QLSYNA7.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QLSYNA7.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/QLSYNA7.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/PSgYzu2.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PSgYzu2.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/PSgYzu2.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/KTQhLMA.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KTQhLMA.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/KTQhLMA.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/R3ajWYS.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/R3ajWYS.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/R3ajWYS.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Jcc3tlg.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Jcc3tlg.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Jcc3tlg.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n這些怒氣又引來一堆小粉紅自幹五表示心靈受創<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/qSDlVSN.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qSDlVSN.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/qSDlVSN.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/DMFngzU.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DMFngzU.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/DMFngzU.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/zN9P68Y.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zN9P68Y.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/zN9P68Y.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n不得不說共產的洗腦太成功<br>\n會上Subtle Asian Traits的都算是比較洋化的亞裔，裡面居然還有一堆自幹五，可見洗腦真的很徹底<br>\n最後借其中一個留言，送給在翻牆偷看的小粉紅:<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/e8tmj05.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/e8tmj05.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/e8tmj05.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n政黨真的與國族無關喔啾咪<br>\n中國自古以來一堆愛國詩人就在批評時政了，杜甫是大漢奸美國走狗&lt;3","date":"2020-04-26","agreeCount":3,"discussionCount":0}